<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>비밀번호 찾기</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,typography"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script>
    tailwind.config = {
      darkMode: "class",
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            primary: "#6366F1", // Indigo 500
            "background-light": "#F9FAFB", // Gray 50
            "background-dark": "#1F2937", // Gray 800
          },
          fontFamily: {
            display: ["Noto Sans KR", "sans-serif"],
          },
          borderRadius: {
            DEFAULT: "0.5rem", // 8px
          },
        },
      },
    };
  </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark font-display text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
<header class="flex justify-between items-center mb-16">
<a class="text-primary font-bold text-xl flex items-center" href="#">
<span class="material-icons mr-2">article</span>
<span>NewsRecomm</span>
</a>
<nav class="flex items-center space-x-4">
<a class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">로그인</a>
<a class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-primary rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors" href="#">회원가입</a>
</nav>
</header>
<main class="max-w-md mx-auto">
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
<div class="text-center mb-8">
<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">비밀번호 찾기</h1>
<p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">가입 시 사용한 아이디와 이메일을 입력해주세요.</p>
</div>
<form action="#" class="space-y-6" method="POST">
<div>
<label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300" for="user-id">아이디</label>
<div class="mt-1">
<input class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-md focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary dark:text-white placeholder-gray-400 dark:placeholder-gray-500" id="user-id" name="user-id" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요" required="" type="text"/>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300" for="email">이메일</label>
<div class="mt-1 flex">
<input autocomplete="email" class="flex-grow px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-l-md focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary dark:text-white placeholder-gray-400 dark:placeholder-gray-500" id="email" name="email" placeholder="이메일 주소를 입력하세요" required="" type="email"/>
<button class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-r-md text-white bg-gray-400 dark:bg-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-500 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-gray-500 transition-colors" type="button">
                인증메일 발송
              </button>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<button class="w-full flex justify-center py-3 px-4 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-white bg-primary hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-primary transition-colors" type="submit">
              비밀번호 찾기
            </button>
</div>
</form>
</div>
<p class="mt-8 text-center text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
<a class="font-medium text-primary hover:text-indigo-500" href="#">홈으로 돌아가기</a>
</p>
</main>
</div>

</body></html>